fLume here again with another map, this time its a ezhop and auto map only this will be very difficult with alot of prespeeding on legit settings so it would be terrible gameplay for that. ONCE AGAIN THIS IS A AUTO/EZ MAP. Fun speed run map made for good times and ez bhopping. Ive been playing alot of auto and decided to make a map specially for it. I will likely make a legit map in the future but this is it for now. If ANYTHING is wrong with the map message me and I will try to fix it as fast as possible.

there are 2 levels green hill themed, and a bonus.

Happy hopping
